    [
      "embed",
      {
        "url": "https://twitter.com/corinne_podger/status/1103270780836687872",
        "html": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Most people aren&#39;t yet using smart speakers (and smartscreens, headphones,  car assistants etc) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nicnewman?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@nicnewman</a> tells <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/newsrw?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#newsrw</a>, partly because they can get audio news elsewhere (including RADIO) and partly because tone &amp; style of dedicated SS content isn&#39;t there yet. <a href=\"https://t.co/qtvgqxN1cx\">pic.twitter.com/qtvgqxN1cx</a></p>&mdash; 𝐂𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐧𝐞 𝐏𝐨𝐝𝐠𝐞𝐫📱🎓 (@corinne_podger) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/corinne_podger/status/1103270780836687872?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 6, 2019</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n",
        "type": "rich"
      }
    ],
    [
      "embed",
      {
        "url": "https://twitter.com/bellaqvist/status/1103272194161946625",
        "html": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Speaking on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/smartspeakers?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#smartspeakers</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nicnewman?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@nicnewman</a> says &quot;people haven’t gotten the content and tone right for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/news?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#news</a> flash briefings yet,” adding that podcasts are not doing as well as maybe thought; &quot;most people use their headphones for that.” Lots of industry tweaking needed, then. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/newsrw?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#newsrw</a></p>&mdash; Bella Qvist (@bellaqvist) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bellaqvist/status/1103272194161946625?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 6, 2019</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n",
