        "url": "https://twitter.com/cushtilla/status/1103292468697681920",
        "html": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">We just announced the launch of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/guardian?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@guardian</a> Voice Lab&#39;s new experiment, The Guardian Briefing. The Briefing combines human rich audio with synthesised voice - &#39;the news you need, when you want it&#39;. Say &quot;Hey Google, Talk to Guardian Briefing&quot;. <a href=\"https://t.co/Cy9ndLsZfV\">https://t.co/Cy9ndLsZfV</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/newsrw?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#newsrw</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/voice?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#voice</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/XRlrKKpASS\">pic.twitter.com/XRlrKKpASS</a></p>&mdash; Dave O&#39;Donnell (@cushtilla) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/cushtilla/status/1103292468697681920?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 6, 2019</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n",
